    "block_id": "page_008:block_073",
    "block_type": "text",
    "text": "• LLM Reasoning. The LLM starts by analyzing the method-level code changes to understand how these modifications address the vulnerability. By integrating the common vulnerability patterns from the CWE description, the developer’s intent from the fix commit message, and the specific code changes, the LLM further infers the root cause of the vulnerability. It then identifies and highlights the precise code blocks in the pre-fix version that are responsible for the vulnerability, providing an explanation for why these blocks are considered vulnerable.",
    "bbox": [
      45.827999114990234,
      388.1790771484375,
      440.4278869628906,
      461.7223815917969
    ],
    "reading_order": 73,
