    "confidence": "medium"
  },
  {
    "page": 8,
    "block_id": "page_008:block_074",
    "block_type": "text",
    "text": "• Structured Output. The final analysis is returned in JSON format and contains the following information: project name, CVE ID, fix commit hash, vulnerable file path, method signature, and identified vulnerable code blocks.",
    "bbox": [
