  {
    "page": 8,
    "block_id": "page_008:block_075",
    "block_type": "text",
    "text": "For a small number of CVEs, the code fixes cannot be explicitly attributed to any specific method. In such cases, due to the lack of effective method-level context, we provide the LLM with code before and after fix, the CVE and the CWE information to help it identify potentially vulnerable code blocks.",
